      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances utility with a premium feel. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss luster, though a careful walk-around will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small, superficial scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing. The alloy wheels are in great shape with no significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable sanctuary; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster from regular use. All interior features, from the heated seats to the premium audio system and sunroof, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean, reflecting a history of consistent maintenance. The car starts promptly, idles smoothly, and the transmission delivers crisp shifts through all gears. We recently replaced the brake pads and performed a full fluid flush to ensure the car is turn-key ready for its next owner. It drives straight, handles predictably, and offers a quiet, composed ride on the highway.",
